headline: ONEOK Declares Quarterly Dividend
summary: The board of directors of ONEOK, Inc. (NYSE: OKE) today declared a quarterly dividend of $1.03 per share, unchanged from the previous quarter, resulting in an annualized dividend of $4.12 per share.
